sets.from sentence: Our model (line 7) sets a new state-of-the-art on the common noun category by gaining 3.6 and 5.6 points in validation and test over the best baseline AS Reader (line 5).

improves.from sentence: The results show that our model (line 8) improves state-of-the-art accuracy by 4 percent absolute on validation and 3.4 on test with respect to the most recent published result (AS Reader) (line 7).
